[SN]TITLE[SN]
Cheltenham Festival 2017 schedule and BBC coverage times

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
The 2017 Cheltenham Festival takes place from 14 to 17 March.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The feature race takes place each day at 15:30 GMT with the festival's showpiece contest, the Gold Cup, taking place on Friday, 17 March.
There will be live coverage of every race across BBC Radio 5 live and 5 live sports extra throughout the four days and live text commentary on the BBC Sport website.
